              <span id="reviewTextContainer54811722" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer4976179358485447220">This is a book to enjoy,to savor, to learn from- I will certainly re-visit it again and again! &quot;Waves-The The Novel (Melody)&quot; entertains and enriches- This Book helps you think outside the box.</span>
  <span id="freeText4976179358485447220" style="display:none">This is a book to enjoy,to savor, to learn from- I will certainly re-visit it again and again! "Waves-The The Novel (Melody)" entertains and enriches- This Book helps you think outside the box.</span>
